title: Recently Remodeled 1 Bedroom in West Hollywood * Stainless Steel Appls
posting_body: ['Larrabee Apartments is located in the heart of the famous sunset strip, offering classic West Hollywood living.', '1111', 'Larrabee is a newly renovated apartment community with new stainless steel appliances, hardwood style floors, granite countertops, and more.', 'Community amenities include a pool and on site laundry.', 'Come take a tour of our community today!', '$100.00 For Parking', 'Virtual Tour Unit 8:\xa0<URL>', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '- Hardwood Style Flooring', '- Window Coverings', '- Granite Countertops', '- Dishwasher', '- Gas Range', '- Refrigerator', '- Air Conditioning', '- Disposal', '- Newly Renovated', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Oversized Closets', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '- Swimming Pool', '- Laundry On-Site', '- Controlled Access/Gated', 'PET POLICY', 'Cats and Dogs Welcome.', 'Additional Fees and Deposit May Apply.', 'Call for Details and Restrictions.', '1111 Larrabee Street', 'West Hollywood, CA', '90069', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Square Footage Is Approximate.', 'Price and availability are subject to change.', "Close to 405 Freeway, Amarone, Boa, Mel's Drive-In, Rainbow Grill, The Viper Room, The Whiskey, Beverly Center Mall, Hollywood High School, Beverly Hills, Beverly Grove, Sunset Strip"]
